    Theory of Computing is a peer-reviewed open access scientific journal covering theoretical computer science. The journal was established in 2005 and is published by the Department of Computer Science of the University of Chicago. The editor-in-chief is L\xc3\xa1szl\xc3\xb3 Babai (University of Chicago).\n
